Text: Jarrod DentistI got a notice from the dentist yesterday that Jarrod has a dental cleaning scheduled for February at I have a doctors appointment that day at and cannot take him can you If not let me know and Ill reschedule his appointment Also I am scheduled to have the boys the weekend of April and would like to switch with you if possible Let me know what would work for you Thanks Joan

RE ThanksHi Glad it went well We all need a bit of optimism right now Give me a call I would be glad to be a sounding board Again I really admire your ability to Lay it on the line do you get the pun to management Joan Original Message From Schwieger Jim Sent Thursday October PM To Collins Joan Subject Thanks Thanks for the nice things you have said over the last week Your knowledge of my personality provides me with a way to see if Im going overboard I met with Cindy Olson this morning They sincerely want to know what I think needs to be done to get employee confidence back I was not timid in my recommendations and I really think they had already thought through a lot of them I came out of it optimistic Cindy is supposed to get back to me hopefully Friday I would like to talk to you about some of my ideas tonight Thanks Swig
